articles.title: Drought is driving elephants closer to people. The consequences can be deadly

articles.title: Honeybee
articles.synopsis: honeybee, (tribe Apini), also spelled honey bee, any of a group of insects in the family Apidae (order Hymenoptera) that in a broad sense includes all bees that make honey.

articles.title: Facts about tardigrades
articles.synopsis: Tardigrades, often called water bears or moss piglets, are near-microscopic aquatic animals with plump, segmented bodies and flattened heads.
